# Tic-Tac-Toe AI

## Objective
Build an AI agent that plays Tic-Tac-Toe against a human player.

## Algorithm Used
Minimax Algorithm

## Features
- Human vs AI gameplay
- AI selects the best move
- Win, lose, and draw detection
- Console-based interface

## Outcome
The AI evaluates possible moves and chooses the optimal move, making it difficult to defeat.

